Guidance on product images from Shopify docs: https://docs.shopify.com/api/product_image#index


  ---> GET ALL IMAGES

  https://wander-feed.myshopify.com/admin/products/3697025351/images.json


  ___________________________________________


  ---> GET A SINGLE IMAGE BY PRODUCT AND IMAGE ID

  GET /admin/products/#{id}/images/#{id}.json


  Example: /admin/products/632910392/images/850703190.json

